snippet.title: Farmyard Survivors - Steam Next Fest: February 2025 Demo
snippet.description:
Survive hordes of cute (but evil) animals attacking your farm in this fast-paced, lane-based roguelite. Recruit adorable heroes and unlock powerful support animals to protect your farm from relentless attackers!

Developed by Viron Games
Release Date: March 17th, 2025
